<script type="text/javascript">
        var srcMap = "https://maps.googleapis.com/maps/api/js?key=" + process.env.GOOGLE_API_KEY + "&callback=initMap"
   </script>
   
   <script async defer src=srcMap type="text/javascript"></script>
  
   <script type="text/javascript" src="https://www.gstatic.com/charts/loader.js"></script>
   
   <script type="text/javascript">
   
        // gauge
   
        var data1 = null;
        var data2 = null;
        var data3 = null;
        
        var option1 = null;
        var option2 = null;
        var option3 = null;
        
        var chart1 = null; 
        var chart2 = null; 
        var chart3 = null; 
        
        google.charts.load('current', {'packages':['gauge', 'map', 'bar', 'corechart', 'line']});
        google.charts.setOnLoadCallback(drawChart);
        
        function drawChart() {
            
            data1 = google.visualization.arrayToDataTable([
              ['Label', 'Value'],
              ['Temperature', 0]
            ]);
            
            data2 = google.visualization.arrayToDataTable([
              ['Label', 'Value'],
              ['Humidity', 0]
            ]);
            
            data3 = google.visualization.arrayToDataTable([
              ['Label', 'Value'],
              ['Pressure', 0]
            ]);
            
            option1 = {
              width: 600, height: 220,
              redFrom: 70, redTo: 100,
              yellowFrom:26, yellowTo: 70,
              minorTicks: 5,
              min: 0, max: 100
            };
            
            option2 = {
              width: 600, height: 220,
              redFrom: 90, redTo: 100,
              yellowFrom:70, yellowTo: 90,
              minorTicks: 5,
              min: 0, max: 100
            };
            
            option3 = {
              width: 600, height: 220,
              redFrom: 900, redTo: 1200,
              yellowFrom:750, yellowTo: 900,
              minorTicks: 5,
              min: 0, max: 1200
            };
            
            chart1 = new google.visualization.Gauge(document.getElementById('chart1_div'));
            chart2 = new google.visualization.Gauge(document.getElementById('chart2_div'));
            chart3 = new google.visualization.Gauge(document.getElementById('chart3_div'));
            
            chart1.draw(data1, option1);
            chart2.draw(data2, option2);
            chart3.draw(data3, option3);
      }
      
      function updateChart(temp, humid, pres) {
          
          data1.setValue(0, 1, temp);// + "C");
          chart1.draw(data1, option1);
          
          data2.setValue(0, 1, humid);// + "%");
          chart2.draw(data2, option2);
          
          data3.setValue(0, 1, pres);// + "kPa");
          chart3.draw(data3, option3);
      }
    </script>
    
   <script type="text/javascript">
   
        // agregate info
      
        function updateAgrGgChart(objSens) {
        
            if(objSens.min_temp !== undefined)
                document.getElementById('mint').innerHTML = objSens.min_temp;
            if(objSens.max_temp !== undefined)
                document.getElementById('maxt').innerHTML = objSens.max_temp;
            if(objSens.min_humidity !== undefined)
                document.getElementById('minh').innerHTML = objSens.min_humidity;
            if(objSens.max_humidity !== undefined)
                document.getElementById('maxh').innerHTML = objSens.max_humidity;
            if(objSens.min_pressure !== undefined)
                document.getElementById('minp').innerHTML = objSens.min_pressure;
            if(objSens.max_pressure !== undefined)
                document.getElementById('maxp').innerHTML = objSens.max_pressure;
        }
    </script>   
    
    <script type="text/javascript">
    
        var dataLnT;
        var dataLnH;
        var dataLnP;
        
        var opsLnT;
        var opsLnH;
        var opsLnP;
        
        var chartLnT;
        var chartLnH;
        var chartLnP;
        
        google.charts.setOnLoadCallback(drawBasic);
        
        function drawBasic() {
            
            dataLnT = new google.visualization.DataTable();
            dataLnT.addColumn('datetime', 'X');
            dataLnT.addColumn('number', 'Temperature');
            
            dataLnH = new google.visualization.DataTable();
            dataLnH.addColumn('datetime', 'X');
            dataLnH.addColumn('number', 'Humidity');
            
            dataLnP = new google.visualization.DataTable();
            dataLnP.addColumn('datetime', 'X');
            dataLnP.addColumn('number', 'Pressure');
            
            opsLnT = {
                hAxis: {
                  title: 'Time',
                  format: 'HH:mm:ss'
                },
                vAxis: {
                  title: 'Temperature'
                },
                curveType: 'function',
                colors:['red','#004411'],
                lineWidth : 3
            };
            
            opsLnH = {
                hAxis: {
                  title: 'Time',
                  format: 'HH:mm:ss'
                },
                vAxis: {
                  title: 'Humidity'
                },
                curveType: 'function',
                colors:['orange','#004411'],
                lineWidth : 3
            };
            
            opsLnP = {
                hAxis: {
                  title: 'Time',
                  format: 'HH:mm:ss'
                },
                vAxis: {
                  title: 'Pressure'
                },
                curveType: 'function',
                lineWidth : 3
            };
            
            chartLnT = new google.visualization.LineChart(document.getElementById('chartLnT_div'));
            chartLnH = new google.visualization.LineChart(document.getElementById('chartLnH_div'));
            chartLnP = new google.visualization.LineChart(document.getElementById('chartLnP_div'));
            
            chartLnT.draw(dataLnT, opsLnT);
            chartLnH.draw(dataLnH, opsLnH);
            chartLnP.draw(dataLnP, opsLnP);
        }
        
        function updateLnChart(temp, humid, pres) {

            dataLnT.addRow([new Date(), temp]);
            chartLnT.draw(dataLnT, opsLnT);
            
            dataLnH.addRow([new Date(), humid]);
            chartLnH.draw(dataLnH, opsLnH);
            
            dataLnP.addRow([new Date(), pres]);
            chartLnP.draw(dataLnP, opsLnP);
        }
        
    </script> 
    
    <script type="text/javascript">
    
        var wsDeviceData;
        var wsAgrData;
        
        var wsDeviceDataUri = "ws:";
        var wsAgrDataUri = "ws:";        
        
        var loc = window.location;
      
        if (loc.protocol === "https:") { 
        
            wsDeviceDataUri = "wss:"; 
            wsAgrDataUri = "wss:"; 
        }
        
        wsDeviceDataUri += "//" + loc.host + loc.pathname.replace("sensors","ws/maindata");
        wsAgrDataUri += "//" + loc.host + loc.pathname.replace("sensors","ws/agrdata");

        function wsDisconnect() {
        
            wsDeviceData.close();
            wsAgrData.close();
        }

        function wsConnect() {
            
            wsDeviceDataConnect();
            wsAgrDataConnect();
        }
        
        var IsModalDlgDispayed = false;
        
        function wsDeviceDataConnect() {
            
            //console.log("connect",wsDeviceDataUri);
            wsDeviceData = new WebSocket(wsDeviceDataUri);
            
            wsDeviceData.onmessage = function(msg) {
                
                var json = msg.data;
                var obj = JSON.parse(json);

                // ST Nucleo
                updateChart(obj.d.A_Temperature, obj.d.A_Humidity, obj.d.A_Pressure);
                
                updateLnChart(obj.d.A_Temperature, obj.d.A_Humidity, obj.d.A_Pressure);
                
                var threshold = 25.8;
                if( parseFloat(obj.d.A_Temperature.toFixed(1)) >= parseFloat(threshold.toFixed(1)) && IsModalDlgDispayed === false) {
                    $("#modalDlg").modal("show");
                    IsModalDlgDispayed = true;
                }

            }
            wsDeviceData.onopen = function() {
            }
            wsDeviceData.onclose = function() {
                wsDeviceData.close();
                setTimeout(function() {
                    wsDeviceDataConnect();
                }, 1000);
            }   
        }
        
        function wsAgrDataConnect() {
            
            wsAgrData = new WebSocket(wsAgrDataUri);
            
            wsAgrData.onmessage = function(msg) {
                
                var json = msg.data;
                var obj = JSON.parse(json);
                
                updateAgrGgChart(obj);
            }
            wsAgrData.onopen = function() {
            }
            wsAgrData.onclose = function() {
                wsAgrData.close();
                setTimeout(function() {
                    wsAgrDataConnect();
                }, 1000);            
            }   
        }
        
    </script>
